x^2 + y^2 = 2, \quad (x-1)^2 + (y+1.5)^2 = 1.
(x-1)^2 + (y + \frac 32)^2 = 1
x^2 - 2x + 1 + y^2 + 3y + \frac 94 = 1
(x^2 + y^2) - 2x + 3y + \frac 94 = 0
2 - 2x + 3y + \frac94 = 0
3y - 2x + \frac{17}{4} = 0
y = \frac{2x - \frac{17}{4}}{3}
x^2 + \left(\frac{2x - \frac{17}{4}}{3}\right)^2 - 2 = 0
x^2 + \frac{4x^2 - 17x + \frac{289}{16}}{9} - 2 = 0
9x^2 + 4x^2 - 17x + \frac{289}{16} - 18 = 0
144x^2 + 64x^2 - 272x + 289 - 288 = 0
208x^2 - 272x + 1 = 0
